OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A top Chinese live-streamer has been   
OL,6, handed a 1.34bn yuan ($210m; #160m)    
OL,7, fine for tax evasion.                  
OL,9,FHuang Wei, known as Viya, is an        
OL,10,Finternet celebrity with tens of        
OL,11,Fmillions of followers. She has used her
OL,12,Fplatform to sell a variety of products.
OL,14,FAuthorities in Hangzhou accuse her of  
OL,15,Fhiding her personal income as well as  
OL,16,Fother financial offences between 2019  
OL,17,Fand 2020.                              
OL,19,FIn a post on her Weibo account, she    
OL,20,Fsaid she was "deeply sorry".           
